## Project Structure (M8)
- com.clc.levelup.config — Security, DataSeed, GlobalModelAttributes  
- com.clc.levelup.controllers — Home, Login/Register, Products, Orders  
- com.clc.levelup.model — User, Role, Product, Order  
- com.clc.levelup.repository — CRUD Repositories (User, Role, Product)  
- com.clc.levelup.service — UserService, AuthService, ProductService  
- com.clc.levelup.security — PasswordResetService, DatabaseUserDetailsService  
- com.clc.levelup.validation — @PasswordMatches, Validator class  
- com.clc.levelup.api — REST API endpoints for /api/products  
- src/test/java — JUnit 5 tests with MockMvc and Spring Security test helpers

